# NotesMozilla
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
On Linux, Mozilla requires JRE 1.4.2 or later.

If you installed the Java Runtime Environment 5.0 Update 6, this plugin is
/usr/java/jrel.5.0_6/plugin/i386/ns7/libjavaplugin_oji.so - and to install it
for Mozilla (including Mozilla Firefox), do the following:

Open a terminal
Change to your Mozilla (or Mozilla Firefox) plugins directory
Issue the following command:

ln -s /usr/java/jdk/jre/plugin/i386/ns7/libjavaplugin_oji.so
